# 📈 Interactive Sales Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📌 Objective
Visualize and explore business sales performance with interactive Power BI dashboards.

## 🧰 Tools Used
Power BI

## 📊 Dataset
Internal sales data (imported into .pbix)

## 🛠️ Methodology
- Loaded and cleaned data within Power BI
- Built relationships across customer, product, and order tables
- Designed dashboards with bar charts, KPIs, slicers, and drill-downs

## 🔍 Key Insights
- Top 5 customers accounted for a significant portion of revenue
- Category B products had the highest margin
- Regional sales trends helped adjust marketing strategies

📂 File: `Portf.pbix`
